cc:Work.dc:title: Tango-style Quake I and II logos
cc:Work.dc:description: Based on the Tango colour palette and <http://tango.freedesktop.org/Tango_Icon_Theme_Guidelines>. Quake I and II box art on Wikipedia was used as a rough guide for the shape, but was not traced.
